<p>The website is organized as follows:</p>
<ul>
  <li>_layouts
    <ul>
      <li>default.html</li>
      <li>post.html</li>
      <li>project.html</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>_includes
    <ul>
      <li>footer.html</li>
      <li>header.html</li>
      <li>navbar.html</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>_data
    <ul>
      <li>navbar.yml</li>
      <li>projects.yml</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>index.html</li>
  <li>â€¦other files</li>
</ul>

<p>Layouts hold default.html, which uses the header, navbar, and fotoer in _includes. Here is a code snippet from navbar.html.</p>

